OL,3,CWelsh Government to announce spending
OL,4,Cplans for next financial year
OL,6,FMark Drakeford will set out the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment's spending plans for the
OL,8,Fnext financial year today (Tuesday) in
OL,9,Fa budget that is unusual in several
OL,10,Fways and likely to be hugely
OL,11,Fcontroversial politically.
OL,13,FIt won't see any significant new
OL,14,Fspending commitments, so there'll be
OL,15,Fno major increases or cuts. But
OL,16,Fopposition parties could block the
OL,17,Fspending plans which could have major
OL,18,Fimplications for public services and
OL,19,Ffor politics ahead of next year's
OL,20,Felection.
