OL,3,CWelsh Government to announce spending
OL,4,Cplans for next financial year
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government spends #26bn each
OL,7,Fyear on services that it has
OL,8,Fresponsibility for here in Wales, such
OL,9,Fas hospitals, schools, roads and the
OL,10,Fenvironment.
OL,12,FMr Drakeford, the Finance Secretary,
OL,13,Fhas already said that he will announce
OL,14,Fa one-year budget rather than a multi-
OL,15,Fyear plan and will simply increase
OL,16,Foverall spending for each department
OL,17,Fby inflation. The draft budget will
OL,18,Falso leave an amount of money
OL,19,Funallocated.
