OL,3,CWelsh Government to announce spending
OL,4,Cplans for next financial year
OL,6,FThat's because this current Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment will come to an end when
OL,8,Fthe Senedd election is held next May.
OL,9,FWhoever is in power after that
OL,10,Felection will then have the
OL,11,Fflexibility to alter the plans in
OL,12,Fwhat's known as a supplementary budget
OL,13,Fin June.
OL,15,FHowever, the Labour government may not
OL,16,Fbe able to pass its budget. Labour has
OL,17,Fexactly half of the voting seats in
OL,18,Fthe Senedd (28) and needs a majority
OL,19,F(29) to get the spending plans through.
