OL,3,CWelsh Government to announce spending
OL,4,Cplans for next financial year
OL,6,FPrevious budgets had been passed
OL,7,Fbecause Plaid Cymru MSs had abstained,
OL,8,Fbut they refused to back the current
OL,9,F(2025/26) spending. In the end, Labour
OL,10,Freached a deal with the only Liberal
OL,11,FDemocrat MS and would hope to repeat
OL,12,Fthat.
OL,14,FHowever, much depends on the outcome
OL,15,Fof the Caerphilly by-election on
OL,16,FOctober 23. If Labour were to lose
OL,17,Fthat seat, it would need two
OL,18,Fopposition votes instead of one.
