OL,3,CWelsh Government to announce spending
OL,4,Cplans for next financial year
OL,6,FThat in turn would lead to a ferocious
OL,7,Fpolitical row. Already Labour accuses
OL,8,Fthe Conservatives and Plaid Cymru of
OL,9,Fjeopardising last year's budget. Those
OL,10,Fparties accuse Labour of failing to
OL,11,Freach out to attempt a deal.
OL,13,FIf this happens again in January, the
OL,14,Ffallout could be huge and could shape
OL,15,Fthe entire direction of the Senedd
OL,16,Felection.
